 ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap482:3.4":{"pli":"pulinassa idaṁ phalaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap482:4.1":{"pli":"Kilesā jhāpitā mayhaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap482:4.2":{"pli":"…pe… ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap482:4.3":{"pli":"viharāmi anāsavo. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap482:5.1":{"pli":"Svāgataṁ vata me āsi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap482:5.2":{"pli":"…pe… ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap482:5.3":{"pli":"kataṁ buddhassa sāsanaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap482:6.1":{"pli":"Paṭisambhidā catasso, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap482:6.2":{"pli":"…pe… ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap482:6.3":{"pli":"kataṁ buddhassa sāsanaṁ”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>"},"tha-ap482:7.1":{"pli":"Itthaṁ sudaṁ āyasmā pulinacaṅkamiyo thero imā gāthāyo abhāsitthāti. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"tha-ap482:8.1":{"pli":"Pulinacaṅkamiyattherassāpadānaṁ dasamaṁ. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p>"},"tha-ap482:9.1":{"pli":"Naḷamālivaggo aṭṭhacattālīsamo. ","html":"<p class='endsection'>{}</p>"},"tha-ap482:10.1":{"pli":"Tassuddānaṁ ","html":"<p class='uddana-intro'>{}</p>"},"tha-ap482:11.1":{"pli":"Naḷamālī maṇidado, ","html":"<blockquote class='uddanagatha'><p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap482:11.2":{"pli":"ukkāsatikabījanī; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap482:11.3":{"pli":"Kummāso ca kusaṭṭho ca, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap482:11.4":{"pli":"giripunnāgiyopi ca. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"tha-ap482:12.1":{"pli":"Vallikāro pānadhido, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap482:12.2":{"pli":"atho pulinacaṅkamo; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"tha-ap482:12.3":{"pli":"Gāthāyo pañcan